The evidence with the title 'Burr, Tillis explain votes to consider ACA rewrite ' says Jul 26, 2017  ... North Carolina 's two U.S. senators say they voted to begin floor debate on legislation to repeal or rewrite the Affordable Care Act because of deep dissatisfaction with the law commonly called Obamacare . Sens. Richard Burr and Thom Tillis were among 50 Republicans who voted for a " motion to proceed"  ... 
